005401_9afee4d981c114276f4816c2a5dbffd1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F15%2F005401_9afee4d981c114276f4816c2a5dbffd1.jpeg&h=da474753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSiri 咪又係chatbot <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未來如果可以做到佢咁就有用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff42cd36e25fd2b60c6154e6043d4b47f507bdc","tid":1972684,"uid":168911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94ab471518d68fab0894ae9c98eb57ffd9611439","tid":1972684,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce909051d25659fc2986c73c0b5b36a479b6bdce","tid":1972684,"uid":168911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:43:35.000Z","msg":"比tips, 戰鬥方法 etc. 咪又係programmer預先製定，呢個世界無魔術<br />\n而家都有架，不過要你用quick menu / keyboard某粒制去做<br />\n<br />\n我諗你係想講用把口就得<br />\nvoice command / natural language既engine 的確無乜game有做過<br />\n但係你要諗既係，你用口講，會快過禁制咩? 好多gamer都未必鐘意出聲<br />\n<br />\n但係VR game會係一個機會去發展呢方面既技術, 因為會更immersive"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:47:01.000Z","msg":"就算唔想quick menu 落指令 太無變化 例如玩cod 想npc 爬上梯 伏地等10秒一齊還火 <br />\n<br />\n呢啲複雜性戰術"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T17:06:28.000Z","msg":"你呢個諗法係好，但都係果句<br />\n而家無game做，其實唔係因為無siri既技術囉。<br />\n口講又好，用quick menu/shortcut key又好，都係programmer一舊舊整出來，唔係一拍個siri落去，個NPC就識做複雜野。<br />\n<br />\n而做左之後，都會有一set有限既指令，並唔會你講乜佢都明<br />\n暫時無乜game會focus係呢方面，因為整game 故事, 畫面, 聲音 都夠大工程，一隻有質素既game，係講緊最少兩年, 有時5,6年以上既製作時間。<br />\n<br />\n不過將來係好可能會有。<br />\n今年岩岩出既Half-Life Alyx就係推進VR既一隻好重要既game"},{"pid":"c75442409d7fae67d3568c47323b8a99b9c3e401","tid":1972684,"uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:43:56.000Z","msg":"技術唔係重點，重點係呢個技術點配合內容同玩法<br />\n<br />\n你要npc可以同你對答如流，每個npc都要完整嘅故事背景，人物設定，對話又要跟劇情推進<br />\n<br />\n否則大部分對答都係唔知道、唔關事、冇實質內容<br />\n<br />\n好似依家啲rpg一味玩大地圖、非線性、開放式，但啲野外內容、支線全部都係塞垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517437fb9fe2ce8a9ad88ce2302967284fe4dee0","tid":1972684,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5c5545d197e3e0ef1fbed667855f3d2a4b22d68","tid":1972684,"uid":10788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"137796f7e0784f407a0dabc4875b6ac6f5e612b3","tid":1972684,"uid":189109,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3d3814425eda4a07955562312924a88679ecbff3","tid":1972684,"uid":231725,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:17:44.000Z","msg":"我：要唔要打昆特牌？<br />\nNPC：我唔係咁清楚喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:22:54.000Z","msg":"實測：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07mDaQh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07mDaQh.png&h=719195fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T16:31:53.000Z","msg":"針對遊戲故事 deta base可以細好多 回答就唔會咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:15:23.000Z","msg":"咁就唔係siri啦<br />\n用siri就係唔想fix死一堆答案<br />\n姐係我問你幾大，問你十幾次<br />\n你又loop堆答案"},{"pid":"e6cb2132bf9aa013839ebc9abc68027304a40181","tid":1972684,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c75442409d7fae67d3568c47323b8a99b9c3e401","tid":1972684,"uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:43:56.000Z","msg":"技術唔係重點，重點係呢個技術點配合內容同玩法<br />\n<br />\n你要npc可以同你對答如流，每個npc都要完整嘅故事背景，人物設定，對話又要跟劇情推進<br />\n<br />\n否則大部分對答都係唔知道、唔關事、冇實質內容<br />\n<br />\n好似依家啲rpg一味玩大地圖、非線性、開放式，但啲野外內容、支線全部都係塞垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:30:41.000Z","msg":"相信未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ae0ee65d993702212e11bdb61696b335cf49ae","tid":1972684,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"517437fb9fe2ce8a9ad88ce2302967284fe4dee0","tid":1972684,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu